import React from 'react'
import './Navigation.css'
import Button from '../../components/Button/Button'

export default function Navigation() {
  return (
    <nav>
      <Button small>
        Profile
      </Button>
      <Button small>
        Projects
      </Button>
      <Button small>
        Contacts
      </Button>
    </nav>
  )
}
